query:
SELECT id, name, plannedVisitDate, plannedVisitTime, address 
FROM tourist_sites 
WHERE tripId = 1 AND (name LIKE '%Bešeňová%' OR name LIKE '%Kalameny%')
ORDER BY id DESC;
